"Crawler" monsters this card points to, except "Acid Crawler", cannot be destroyed by battle, gain 300 ATK and DEF, and can make up to 2 attacks on monsters during each Battle Phase. If this face-up card is destroyed by battle, or leaves the field because of an opponent's card effect while its owner controls it: You can target 2 "Crawler" monsters with different names in your GY, except "Acid Crawler"; Special Summon them in face-down Defense Position.
